<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Learn more about our company, mission, and values.">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
        }
        .team {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .team-member {
            flex: 1 1 calc(33.333% - 20px);
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .team-member img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        footer {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Us</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <section>
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>
                Welcome to {{companyName}}! We started with a vision to [insert your mission or purpose here]. 
                Over the years, we've grown into a team passionate about delivering exceptional [products/services].
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                Our mission is to [insert mission statement]. We are committed to innovation, quality, and making a positive impact on the world.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
            <div class="team">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Team Member 1">
                    <h3>John Doe</h3>
                    <p>CEO & Founder</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Team Member 2">
                    <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                    <p>Chief Operating Officer</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100" alt="Team Member 3">
                    <h3>Emily Johnson</h3>
                    <p>Head of Marketing</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
